{"tid":566073,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（百萬火急！）香港去台中package 半價求收留","createTime":"2018-02-19T15:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T07:42:48.000Z","uid":56384,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c590882f16c766260ebe8f71cda1bf0826f4c42c","tid":566073,"uid":56384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港去台中21號出發24號回港+3晚住宿，願意半價$2000（甚至可更低可議）放出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> book曬所有野，想一個人出走，點知！仆街今日先知香港21號公司有大件野走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩錢都退唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但求有人收留，以致唔洗肉痛得咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n21-24香港-台中hkexpress <br />\n1 female box design hotel <br />\n希望可以搵到名類似嘅巴絲搏改到名<br />\n<br />\n有意可留名留telegram 再講details<br />\n<br />\n大恩不言謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有想一人浪漫出走嘅巴絲收留個package<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0050b6045c3e07a08aeb755698dc950fc77a59d","tid":566073,"uid":7854,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"收定皮都得 hkexpress絕對無得改名"},{"pid":"a2932752a2ed510afb3d9fa6f9c684704c88d131","tid":566073,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/231655_2f3380f6199892a7d03b9ec5290f8bf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F231655_2f3380f6